---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CTA from '../components/ui/CTA.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Local SEO – Get Found on Google | Bluebird"
	description="Done-for-you Local SEO: Google Business Profile setup, local keywords, monthly reports. Growth $499/mo, Authority $699/mo. Add after your website launches."
	canonicalURL="/local-seo"
	keywords="Local SEO, Google Business Profile, local search, get found on Google, Bluebird"
>
	<section class="relative pt-28 sm:pt-32 md:pt-36 pb-20 sm:pb-24 md:pb-32 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-bg overflow-hidden">
		<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-accent/3 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
		<div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<header class="mb-12 sm:mb-16">
				<h1 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text mb-4">
					Local SEO
				</h1>
				<p class="font-body text-lg text-textMuted max-w-2xl">
					We build your website, then help local customers find it. Google Business Profile setup, local keyword optimization, monthly reports—done for you. Add Local SEO after launch, or if you already have a site and want to show up better on Google.
				</p>
			</header>

			<!-- Two tiers -->
			<h2 class="font-headline text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-6">Two tiers, no decision fatigue</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16">
				<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-accentSubtle/30 p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-sm">
					<h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">Growth</h3>
					<p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">$499 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-textMuted">/month</span></p>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-textMuted mb-6">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 text-accent mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
							Google Business Profile setup & optimization
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 text-accent mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
							Local keyword research & on-page optimization
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 text-accent mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
							Monthly reports
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 text-accent mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
							Done-for-you management
						</li>
					</ul>
					<CTA href="/contact" variant="dark" size="sm">Get started</CTA>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-sm text-white">
					<h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Authority</h3>
					<p class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">$699 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-400">/month</span></p>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-300 mb-6">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 text-accent mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
							Everything in Growth
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 text-accent mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
							Deeper local strategy & more visibility
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 text-accent mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
							Monthly reports included
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 text-accent mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
							Priority support
						</li>
					</ul>
					<CTA href="/contact" variant="primary" size="sm">Get started</CTA>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- FAQ-style -->
			<div class="rounded-2xl bg-accent/5 border border-accent/10 p-6 sm:p-8 mb-12">
				<h2 class="font-headline text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Common questions</h2>
				<details class="group border-b border-accentSubtle/30 pb-4 mb-4 last:border-0 last:pb-0 last:mb-0">
					<summary class="font-body text-base font-medium text-text cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
						How do I make my business appear on Google?
						<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-textMuted group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
					</summary>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-textMuted mt-3 leading-relaxed">
						We set up and optimize your Google Business Profile (GBP), work on local keywords, and manage your local presence month to month. You get monthly reports so you can see what’s happening. We don’t guarantee specific rankings—no one can—but we focus on visibility and helping local customers find you.
					</p>
				</details>
				<details class="group border-b border-accentSubtle/30 pb-4 mb-4 last:border-0 last:pb-0 last:mb-0">
					<summary class="font-body text-base font-medium text-text cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
						Do you guarantee rankings?
						<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-textMuted group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
					</summary>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-textMuted mt-3 leading-relaxed">
						No. No one can guarantee rankings—Google’s algorithm changes, and local competition varies. We focus on what we can control: a solid GBP, local optimization, and consistent work. Monthly reports show you the progress.
					</p>
				</details>
			</div>

			<div class="text-center">
				<p class="font-body text-sm text-textMuted mb-4">Ready to get found? Add Local SEO after your website, or start if you already have a site.</p>
				<CTA href="/contact" variant="primary" size="md" showArrow={true}>
					Get in touch
				</CTA>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<Footer />
</Layout>
